  "detailed_description": "Twisted:EE is a clever action-platformer game combined with the best gameplay elements like time and object manipulation, clever enemies, traps and other challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690410/extras/7e056189b9a72a5a0699c0ad84b3ab4b.poster.avif?t=1594380892\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690410/extras/7e056189b9a72a5a0699c0ad84b3ab4b.webm?t=1594380892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690410/extras/7e056189b9a72a5a0699c0ad84b3ab4b.mp4?t=1594380892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Made by one person<br></li><li>Short but very hard<br></li><li>There is no story, only gameplay<br></li><li>Gravity gun<br></li><li>Time manipulation<br></li><li>Jetpack</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the Enhanced Edition</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Built in achievements / challenges<br></li><li>New starting area, new enemies<br></li><li>Upgraded menu system<br></li><li>New post-processing<br></li><li>New player UI</li></ul>",
